         = Multi-camera\n| runtime              = 43 minutes\n| company              = Lingo Pictures\n| network              = [[Network Ten]]\n| picture_format       = [[576i]] ([[SDTV]])<br/>[[1080i]] ([[high-definition television|HDTV]]) \n| audio_format         = Stereo\n| related              = \n| first_aired          = {{Start date|2020|04|22|df=y}}\n| last_aired           = <!--- {{end date| | |df=y}} --->\n| website              = https://10play.com.au/the-secrets-she-keeps\n| production_website   = https://www.lingopictures.com/the-secret-she-keeps\n}}\n\n'''''The Secrets She Keeps''''' is an [[Australia]]n [[psychological thriller]] [[Drama (film and television)|drama]] television series that will officially premiere on [[Network Ten]] on 22 April 2020 at 8:45pm<ref>{{cite web|last=Knox|first=David|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2020/04/airdate-the-secrets-she-keeps.html|title=Airdate: The Secrets She Keeps|date=8 April 2020|website=TV Tonight|publisher=TV Tonight|accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref>, but was released prematurely [[Network Ten#10 Play|10 Play]] on 4 April 2020 as a result of the [[2019-20 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Knox|first=David|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2020/04/10-play-the-secrets-she-keeps.html|title=10 Play: The Secrets She Keeps|date=5 April 2020|publisher=TV Tonight|accessdate=7 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Knox|first=David|url=https://10play.com.au/the-secrets-she-keeps/articles/binge-psychological-thriller-the-secrets-she-keeps-now-on-10-play/tpa200403ejbyd|title=Binge Psychological Thriller The Secrets She Keeps Now On 10 Play|date=4 April 2020|website=[[10 Play (Network Ten)|10 Play]]|publisher=[[Network Ten]]|accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref> The six-part series is set in the [[Blue Mountains (New South Wales)|Blue Mountains]] and is about two women from vastly different backgrounds with explosive secrets that could destroy everything they hold dear.<ref name=\"10 Program\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2019/05/cameras-roll-on-secret-bridesmaids-business.html/|title=Cameras roll on 'The Secrets She Keeps' for Ten|last=Knox|first=David|date=20 May 2018|work=TV Tonight|accessdate=20 May 2018}}</ref>\nThe series is written by [[Sarah Walker (Australian author)|Sarah Walker]] and Jonathan Gavin, based on the psychological thriller novel by [[Michael Robotham]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://10daily.com.au/entertainment/tv/a190519wiosb/tv-adaptation-of-bestselling-mummy-blog-drama-the-secrets-she-keeps-coming-to-10-20190519|title=TV Adaptation Of Bestselling Mummy Blog Drama 'The Secrets She Keeps' Coming To 10|last=Whitehead|first=Mat|date=19 May 2019|work=10 Daily|accessdate=8 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Laura Carmichael]] as Agatha\n* [[Jessica De Gouw]] as Meghan\n* [[Michael Dorman]] as Jack\n* [[Ryan Corr]] as Simon\n* Michael Sheasby as Hayden\n* Eva Greenwood as Lucy\n\n==Episodes==\n{{Episode table |total_width= |background=#aaaaaa |overall= |title= |director= |writer= |airdate= |prodcode= |country=Australia |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 1\n |RTitle          = Episode 1\n |DirectedBy      = Catherine Millar\n |WrittenBy       = Sarah Walker\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|04|22}}\n |ProdCode        = 359917\u22121\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = aaa\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 2\n |RTitle          = Episode 2\n |DirectedBy      = Catherine Millar\n |WrittenBy       = Sarah Walker\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|04|29}}\n |ProdCode        = 359917\u22122\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = aaa\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 3\n |RTitle          = Episode 3\n |DirectedBy      = Jen Leacey\n |WrittenBy       = Jonathan Gavin\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|05|06}}\n |ProdCode        = 359917\u22123\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = aaa\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 4\n |RTitle          = Episode 4\n |DirectedBy      = Jen Leacey\n |WrittenBy   