{"title_page": "Degree Colleges in Kashmir", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}}\n{{Orphan|date=December 2017}}\n\nThere are about 47 Government and 3 Private Grant-in-Aid degree colleges in Kashmir province, of Indian administrated state of [[Jammu and Kashmir]] as per the data available by Jammu and Kashmir  Higher Education Department. The colleges in Kashmir province are located in 10 districts. These districts include, [[Srinagar district|Srinagar]], [[Baramulla district|Baramulla]], [[Anantnag district|Anantnag]], [[Budgam district|Budgam]], [[Kupwara district|Kupwara]], [[Pulwama district|Pulwama]], [[Ganderbal district|Ganderbal]], [[Kulgam district|Kulgam]], [[Shopian district|Shopian]] and [[Bandipora district|Bandipora]].<ref>{{Cite web|title = Department of Higher Education, Government of Jammu & Kashmir|url = http://www.jkhighereducation.nic.in/government_colleges.html|website = www.jkhighereducation.nic.in|accessdate = 2015-11-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140824074807/http://jkhighereducation.nic.in/government_colleges.html|archive-date = 24 August 2014|url-status = dead}}</ref> All the degree colleges of [[Kashmir]] province are affiliated to the [[University of Kashmir]].\n\n== District wise breakup of colleges<ref>{{Cite web|title = List of Colleges|url = http://www.jkhighereducation.nic.in/government_colleges.html|website = www.jkhighereducation.nic.in|accessdate = 2015-11-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140824074807/http://jkhighereducation.nic.in/government_colleges.html|archive-date = 24 August 2014|url-status = dead}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Affiliated Degree  Colleges|url = http://www.kashmiruniversity.net/Colleges.aspx|website = University of Kashmir|publisher = |accessdate = 2015-11-03}}</ref> ==\n\n=== District Srinagar ===\n\n* [[Sri Pratap College]]\n* [[Amar Singh College]]\n* [[Government College for Women, M.A. Road Srinagar|Women's College, M.A Road]]\n* [[Government College for Women, Nawakadal Srinagar|Women's College, Nawakadal]]\n*[[Islamia College of Science and Commerce, Srinagar|Islamia College of Science &]] \n[[Islamia College of Science and Commerce, Srinagar|Commerce, Hawal]]\n* [[Gandhi Memorial College, Srinagar|Gandhi Memorial College, Fateh Kadal]]\n*[[Vishwa Bharti Women's College, Srinagar|Vishwa Baharti Women's College, Rainawari]]\n* [[Government Degree College, Bemina|Govt. Degree College, Bemina]]\n* Govt. Degree College, Bagi Dilawar Khan\n* College of Nursing, M A Road Srinagar\n\n=== District Baramulla ===\n\n* Govt. Degree College, Baramulla\n* Women's College, Baramulla\n* Govt. Degree College, Sopore\n* Women's College, Sopore\n* Govt. Degree College, Uri\n* Govt. Degree College, Pattan\n* [[Govt Degree College Hadipora]]\n* Govt. Degree College, Tangmarg                                   \n  Govt. Degree College, Kreeri\n\n=== District Anantnag ===\n\n*Govt. Degree College, Anantnag\n*Govt. College for Women, Anantnag\n*Govt. Degree College, Bijbehara\n*Govt. Degree College, Dooru\n* [[:Government Degree College, Kokernag]]\n*Govt. Degree College, Uttersoo\n*Govt Degree College, Vailoo, Larnoo\n\n==== District Budgam ====\n*Govt. Sheikh-ul-Alam Memorial College, Budgam\n*Govt. Degree College, Chadoora\n*Govt. Degree College, Beerwah\n*Govt. Degree College, Charar-i-Sharief\n*Govt. Degree College, Khansahib\n*Govt. Degree College, Magam \n* Govt. Degree College, Soibugh\n\n=== District Kupwara ===\n*Govt.Degree College, Kupwara\n*Govt.Degree College, Handwara\n*Govt. Degree College, Tangdhar\n*Govt. Degree College, Sogam\n*Govt Degree College Women, Kupwara\n\n=== District Pulwama ===\n*[[Govt.Degree College   Pulwama|Govt. Degree College, Pulwama]]\n*Govt. Degree College, Tral\n*Govt. College Women, Pulwama\n*Govt. Degree College, Pampore\n\n<br />\n\n*Govt. Degree College, Awantipora\n*Govt. Degree College, Rajpora\n*Govt. College Women, Tral\n*Govt. Degree College, Kakapora\n\n=